data.description: Charming 2BR+Den/2BA home featuring an open layout in the popular community of Tres Pueblos. This D R Horton built property features a split bedroom layout, high ceilings, ceramic tile flooring, open kitchen with center island, two separate pantries and GE Appliances, private primary bedroom with walk-in closet, low care North facing backyard with a covered patio, dual pane windows throughout, ceiling fans, washer / dryer included and directly out the front door is the recently remodeled breathtaking Tres Pueblos park with basketball court, green grass, mature trees for shade, charcoal grills, canopy / sitting areas and playground equipment.  The Tres Pueblos community is conveniently located near 1-10, the Tucson airport, shopping / restaurants, Sunnyside high school & U of A Tech Park.
